<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<I c="LootActions" i="action" m="interactions.utils.loot" n="loot_WorldEp21_AskAboutRobinHood" s="490280">
  <L n="loot_actions">
    <V t="notification_and_dialog">
      <U n="notification_and_dialog">
        <V n="dialog" t="notification">
          <U n="notification">
            <V n="icon" t="enabled">
              <V n="enabled" t="participant">
                <U n="participant">
                  <L n="participant_type">
                    <E>TargetSim</E>
                  </L>
                </U>
              </V>
            </V>
            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x48B09544<!--String: "The Royal Robber...oh yeah, I've heard about that. The mother of the neighbor of my uncle's best friend saw them once at a bar in Verdemar."--></T>
                  <T>0xD71B2BF0<!--String: "Oh I've heard plenty of stories about this robber. They only ever target rich people, or at least that's what everyone says."--></T>
                  <T>0x377F8E7D<!--String: "A mysterious figure that steals from the rich of Ondarion and gives to the poor...a little too convenient, isn't it? I'm sure they have friends in the pirate neighborhood."--></T>
                  <T>0xBFF97D4B<!--String: "I mean, it's got to be a scam right? Like, who would steal valuables just to give them away? I wouldn't be surprised if it was the doing of a very bored Noble."--></T>
                  <T>0x141AE326<!--String: "Oh gosh...Yes! The stories are true! I saw them with my own eyes. Don't tell anyone, but they once helped a friend of mine when he was running low on funds. Rumour says they hang out at a Bar in Verdemar sometimes."--></T>
                  <T>0xD6ED2D02<!--String: "Oh yeah the stories are certainly real. But it's definitely not just one person. A whole band is out there, seemingly trying to make Ondarion a fairer place. "--></T>
                  <T>0x19CA973D<!--String: "I know nothing about it. But if I had to guess where to find scoundrels like that, I bet they would hang out at some bar in Verdemar, likely in the afternoons."--></T>
                  <T>0x293B5A3E<!--String: "Ha! Don't believe anyone that says they don't know anything about it. We all know a Noble or two who's been robbed by them, it's an open secret."--></T>
                  <T>0xFDB8B301<!--String: "Why are you asking <i>me</i>? Do I look like a criminal to you? ...Well fine, I've heard that someone in Verdemar is friends with them. Don't tell anyone!"--></T>
                  <T>0x94E89DBB<!--String: "Whoever they are, they're definitely dangerous...but also quite popular in Ondarion. I'm sure someone like that must have friends helping them in Verdemar."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
    <V t="buff">
      <U n="buff">
        <U n="buff">
          <T n="buff_type">490281<!--Buff: buff_Ep21World_Landmarks_AskAboutRobinHoodCooldown--></T>
        </U>
      </U>
    </V>
  </L>
</I>